{"id":"es_ES","ocurrence":3,"type":"STRING","value":"Las lentes de categoría 2, medianamente coloreadas, deben utilizarse en días de luminosidad solar mediana"},{"id":"es_ES","ocurrence":4,"type":"STRING","value":"Las lentes de categoría 3 son muy coloreadas, por lo que son las más recomendables para la luminosidad solar fuerte, propia de las zonas de playa y montaña."},{"id":"es_ES","ocurrence":5,"type":"STRING","value":"Las lentes de categoría 4, muy oscuras, sólo deben utilizarse en situaciones de luminosidad extrema, como cuando se practica esquí o actividades de alta montaña."},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"Category 3 polarised filters. The category indicates the level of protection from sunlight. Lenses are categorised into 5 groups:"},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":1,"type":"STRING","value":"Category 0 lenses are very lightly tinted and therefore their use should be limited to indoors or cloudy days."},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":2,"type":"STRING","value":"Category 1 lenses are slightly tinted and are suitable for days with weak sunlight."},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":3,"type":"STRING","value":"Category 2 lenses have a medium tint and should be used on days with average sunlight brightness"},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":4,"type":"STRING","value":"Category 3 lenses have a dark tine and are therefore recommended for strong sunlight, in areas such as the beach or mountains."},{"id":"en_GB","ocurrence":5,"type":"STRING","value":"Category 4 lenses, which have a very dark tint, should only be used for exceptional levels of sunlight, for example, when skiing or for mountain climbing."},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":0,"type":"STRING","value":"Filtres polarisants de catégorie 3. La catégorie indique le niveau de protection des rayons solaires. Il existe 5 catégories :"},{"id":"fr_FR","ocurrence":1,"type":"STRING","value":"Les verres solaires de catégorie 0 sont très clairs. Ils sont recommandés pour être portés en intérieur ou en cas de ciel couvert."},{"id":"f